Distribution. Western Atlantic—USA (North Carolina, Gulf of Mexico), Antilles, Venezuela , and Brazil (Fernando de Noronha, Abrolhos, Maranhão , Piauí , Ceará , Rio Grande do Norte , Paraíba , Pernambuco , Alagoas , Sergipe , Bahia , São Paulo , Santa Catarina) ( Wagner 1990 ; Melo 1996 ;
Mantelatto et al. 2004b
; Young & Serejo 2005 ;
Almeida et al. 2007b
;
Alves et al. 2008
;
Felder et al. 2009
;
Pachelle et al. 2016
;
Mendonça et al . 2019
).

Remarks. Previous records on the coast of São Paulo include Ubatuba (
Mantelatto et al. 2004b
;
Alves et al. 2012b
, 2013b ;
Assugeni et al. 2017
), Ilha Vitória (
Alves et al. 2012a
), and Laje de Santos, Santos (
Assugeni et al. 2017
) lacking the specific collecting point. This species was recorded in Brazil as
Mithrax forceps
(see
Coelho et al . 2008
for references). Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 2976—16S ( MF490193 ), COI ( MF490099 ) (
Mantelatto et al. 2018a
